timeline

    title Automation Maturity Progression

    section Stage 0 &mdash; Primitive script
        Single-use helper : Hard-coded paths
                          : No error handling
                          : No logging
                          : Works on author's machine

    section Stage 1 &mdash; Parameterised
        Arguments and config : Inputs as args / env vars
                             : Removes hard-coded values
                             : Still continues past failures
                             : Still no logging

    section Stage 2 &mdash; Fail-fast
        Strict error handling : set -euo pipefail (bash)
                              : Explicit exceptions (Python)
                              : Bad halt beats silent corruption
                              : Informative error messages

    section Stage 3 &mdash; Observable
        Structured logging : Run identity logged
                          : Arguments and outcome
                          : Decision points logged
                          : Queryable run history

    section Stage 4 &mdash; Idempotent
        Desired-state design : Ensure X exists vs create X
                             : Re-run produces same state
                             : Partial completion recoverable
                             : Recovery scenarios use re-run

    section Stage 5 &mdash; Preflight + Scoped
        Explicit assumptions : Requirements block documented
                             : Preflight validates at start
                             : Least-privilege execution
                             : Service accounts for shared use

    section Stage 6 &mdash; Graduated Tool
        Proper CLI tool : Configuration layering
                        : Distinct exit codes
                        : Structured output (--json)
                        : Distributed as versioned package
                        : Integration tests
